 If I'm going to harness 
 the power of belief,

22
00:01:12,204 --> 00:01:15,573
 I need to find a good way
 to study belief and behavior.

23
00:01:15,574 --> 00:01:19,310
 So I'm paying a visit to UCLA's
 Dr. Aaron Blaisdell,

24
00:01:19,311 --> 00:01:21,279
 who I worked with
 on last season's

25
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:23,748
 "Greater Good"
 Trolley Problem episode.

26
00:01:23,749 --> 00:01:25,650
 ( train whistle blowing )

27
00:01:25,651 --> 00:01:27,919
Dr. Blaisdell,
great to see you again.

28
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,387
Nice to see you again,
Michael.

